436
00:24:44,410 --> 00:24:46,880
Mister Lipa,
with all due respect,

437
00:24:46,950 --> 00:24:50,350
comparing this hospital
with Auschwitz,
it's ridiculous.

438
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:52,680
FT28 has been proven
safe in hundreds...

439
